  message: {fileID: 473}
  isToUpperCase: 1
  messages:
  - Drifting fast and doing burnouts had never been so fun! Burn the asphalt of this open world city!
  - Upgrading your car typically requires the use of aftermarket parts!
  - Before you go ahead and get performance upgrades for your car!
  - Are you Ready for an Upgrade?
  - When you combine the right tires with the right rims, you can upgrade both the look and performance of your vehicle!
  - Earn points, unlock prizes, and feel the adrenaline in limited-time racing events and racing passes
  - Pick your car, customise its body paint, the rims, and wheels or apply different-looking body parts to race with around the world.
